title: [Ta'Illistim, Mzaarine Bazaar]
description: Small owls perch atop lamp posts, hooting loudly in the relative quiet of the nighttime bazaar.  Several passersby pause to admire the beautiful flower beds outside a green tile-roofed shop.
Timid sparrows perch atop lamp posts, warbling meekly above the bustle of the bazaar.  A slender gardener tends to several beautiful flower beds outside a green tile-roofed shop.
